{"tid":856138,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"World War Z 2 有望2019年開拍","createTime":"2018-10-10T11:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T04:43:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f698efeedb33cc57e0b2052891e2ac298e1a382d","tid":856138,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"活屍片《末日之戰》於2013年上映，一直以來都傳出要拍攝續集，但遲遲沒有下文，近來製片之一的Dede Gardner確定續集將在2019年6月開拍，男主角布萊德彼特（Brad Pitt）也會回歸演出。<br />\n<br />\n其實《末日之戰》首集開拍前也遭遇許多挫折，本片改編自Max Brooks的同名小說，2011年投入製作，接連遇到槍枝被布達佩斯當局沒收、延期開拍、劇本改寫等狀況，最後預算為1.9億元，好在最後成果亮眼，不只評價不錯，全球票房更高達5.4億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然派拉蒙影業早就打算製作續集，但直到新的高層於2017年上任後，才推動發展，大衛芬奇（David Fincher）也還忙碌於Netflix的《Mindhunter》。如今Dede Gardner在電影《Beautiful Boy》的紅毯上向《綜藝報》（Variety）證實，續集會在2019年6月拍攝，但這也代表最快要到2020年才會上映。<br />\n<br />\nDede Gardner也透露，除了布萊德彼特會回歸外，還找來大衛芬奇執導，不過目前由Dennis Kelly負責的劇本尚未完成，即使如此，他依然抱持樂觀態度，對目前為止的狀況感到相當滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1278011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1278011&d=bRC2wlJYkrn6cLtypM40fbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=0a4a41c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1278011</a>"},{"pid":"aa11101de06022bab7f464e7cba893589c5e128f","tid":856138,"uid":38672,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"最好睇既喪屍電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3a087d5a8abd8b5fd6044d9ed1d4ffe1640ec2","tid":856138,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"去俄羅斯果段拍左無出街"},{"pid":"9cafdcc24b777830c77f301535f472e2ff3eba8f","tid":856138,"uid":151333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bc17394dc6fa057e71d316a167ca188b13e040","tid":856138,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi